The parameters describing SEI resistance (
R
ct 1
) and the related non-ideal capacitance parameters (
Q 1
) were calculated by analysing the real and imaginary impedances, respectively in mid frequency region. On the other hand, charge transfer resistance (
R
ct 2
) and the related non-ideal capacitance parameters (
Q 2
) were calculated at low frequency range.
